sentences: Erlend Bratland (born 27 October 1991 in Husnes, Kvinnherad, Norway) is a Norwegian singer.
Best known for winning Norske Talenter 2008, a Norwegian television talent series.
Bratland was born to Kjersti Bratland, a native of Husnes, in 1991.
He moved to Haugesund in his teens to study food and restaurant management, but dropped out during his first year to continue his music career.
